&lt;p&gt;Waypoint Management is growing! We are searching for top talent who can contribute to an exceptional living experience for our residents. We have a terrific career opportunity for a &lt;strong&gt;Maintenance Technician &lt;/strong&gt;to join our team of talented property professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a maintenance technician, you will be an integral part of the management team at one of the dynamic communities we operate. You should have a keen eye for detail, an outgoing personality, and the desire to provide our residents with best-in-class customer service.&amp;nbsp; As a member of the Waypoint Management Services team, you will be creating a welcoming community environment for our residents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return, we offer a competitive salary and benefits package, and a platform where your contributions will be recognized and celebrated. If this sounds like an attractive career and growth path for you, please apply.&lt;/p&gt;
