&lt;li&gt;Guarantee units are move in ready and presentable. Review make-ready condition with contractors on an ongoing basis.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete preventive maintenance on HVAC units and other community equipment on a regular basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guarantee 24-hour resolution to priority work orders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for performing plumbing, general maintenance and repairs on property equipment and community structures, in addition to performing grounds maintenance and carpentry functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate within OSHA standards and company safety polices. Keep informed of safety standards, operating policies, and practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all gated entrances and security service equipment are always operable and report if in need of repair.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain the trash compactor and pool service, checking the pool and completing chemical readings&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
