&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An ability to perform on a variety of equipment components, building maintenance, and assist with basic grounds keeping.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability during on-call schedule.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of service supplies, equipment, and materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in repairing buildings and equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
